name: Population dynamics of Mesopodopsis slabberi in the Western Scheldt between 1990 and 1991
description: Density and length-frequency data from Mesopodopsisslabberi sampled between May 1990 and December 1991 for 14 stations in the Western Scheldt. The datawere digitized by VLIZ from the original report: Uppabullung, A. (1999). Population dynamics of the mysid, Mesopodopsis slabberi (Crustaceae,Mysidaceae). MSc Thesis. RUG: Gent. 60 pp.
